val.title: Bay West Mixed Use Project

details.General Plan Land Use: Downtown Dublin Zoning District - Transit-Oriented District
details.Specific Plan Area: Downtown Dublin Zoning District - Transit-Oriented District

Applicant.name: Bay West Development
Applicant.address: 2 Henry Adams St, #450, San Francisco, CA 94103

val.description: The BayWest apartment project is comprised of a 313-unit apartment building with structured parking and 17,000 square feet of ground-floor commercial uses facing Dublin Boulevard on 4.9 acres. The project is on the southeast corner of Dublin Boulevard and Golden Gate Drive. The project also includes site and frontage streetscape improvements along Dublin Boulevard, Golden Gate Drive, and St. Patrick Way.
